mmc: omap_hsmmc: Use OMAP_HSMMC_SUPPORTS_DUAL_VOLT flag to remove host->id based hardcoding

Use OMAP_HSMMC_SUPPORTS_DUAL_VOLT flag instead of host->id
for identifying SD bus voltage capabilities.

